    if not base or not active or len(base) != len(active) or len(base[0]) != len(active[0]):
        return []
    return [[32 if a == 32 else b // (32 - a) for b, a in zip(base_row, active_row)] for base_row, active_row in zip(base, active)]

        matrix_map(
            lambda row, col: ite(
                active[col][row] == 32,
                32,
                base[col][row] // (32 - active[col][row]),
            ),
            base,
            active,
        )
    )
